{"_id":"c61b3d81f18c4fc6","name":"Frosted","type":"condition","img":"icons/svg/frozen.svg","system":{"label":"Frosted","category":"magic","description":"-   Ice has formed on skin and clothing, movement impaired\n-   Movement speed: Halved\n-   Clumsy condition active\n-   Duration: 1 minute unless specified otherwise\n**Recovery:**\n-   Automatically ends after 1 minute\n-   Fire damage or intense heat: Immediate recovery\n-   Can attempt Fortitude save at end of each turn (2 successes ends condition)","tokenIcon":"icons/svg/frozen.svg","activeEffects":[],"stacking":"replace","severity":"moderate","overlayPriority":20,"recovery":{"trigger":"endOfTurn","removeOnSuccess":true,"save":{"type":"fortitude"},"promptPlayer":true,"chatMessage":"Make a Fortitude save to recover from Frosted"},"appliesConditions":["Clumsy"]},"flags":{},"_key":"!items!c61b3d81f18c4fc6","effects":[]}
{"_id":"1b62206fbcde485e","name":"Frozen","type":"condition","img":"icons/svg/frozen.svg","system":{"label":"Frozen","category":"magic","description":"-   Body encased in ice or frozen solid\n-   Restrained condition active \n-   Take 1d8 cold damage  at the end of your turn (frostbite)\n-   Duration: Until ice breaks or melts\n**Escaping Frozen:**\n-   Self: Use 1 [Action] to make Athletics check\n    -   2 successes: Break free completely\n    -   1 success: Damage the ice, subtract 1 from next attempt\n    -   0 successes: Remain Frozen\n-   Ally: Can make Athletics check to break ally free (same thresholds)\n-   Fire damage of 8+: Automatic freedom\n-   Time: Melts naturally after 10 minutes (environmental temperature dependent)","tokenIcon":"icons/svg/frozen.svg","activeEffects":[],"stacking":"replace","severity":"moderate","overlayPriority":20,"damageTick":{"frequency":"endOfTurn","formula":"1d8","showInChat":true,"chatMessage":"Take 1d8 cold damage from Frozen"},"appliesConditions":["Restrained"]},"flags":{},"_key":"!items!1b62206fbcde485e","effects":[]}
